# Architecture stack

Use:
- Turborepo or equivalent monorepo
- Next.js App Router + TypeScript for learner/admin web
- NestJS + TypeScript for API
- PostgreSQL + Prisma for source-of-truth data
- Meilisearch for search projection
- Redis + BullMQ for background jobs
- Socket.IO for realtime battle
- MinIO/S3-compatible storage for media

Keep modules explicit: auth/profile, content, search, flashcards, study, quiz, battle, daily, analytics, admin, media, i18n, notifications, privacy, ops.
